(70, 36, 0, 1, '<p>The RSS link has been added to the sidebar now, to the right of your board''s name. FYI, it will not appear for private boards because RSS does not have any kind of authentication mechanism, and so I have no way to know if the RSS client is allowed to see the content or not.</p>\n<p>The ability to mention / notify users with the @ symbol is now working for replies. I am still working on integrating it for topics.</p>\n<p><a href="https://www.grokbb.com/user/view/6">@#!</a> might like this :)</p>\n<p>Still working on the Who is Online feature too ...</p>\n', 'The RSS link has been added to the sidebar now, to the right of your board''s name. FYI, it will not appear for private boards because RSS does not have any kind of authentication mechanism, and so I have no way to know if the RSS client is allowed to see the content or not.\n\nThe ability to mention / notify users with the @ symbol is now working for replies. I am still working on integrating it for topics.\n\n[@#!](https://www.grokbb.com/user/view/6) might like this :)\n\nStill working on the Who is Online feature too ...', 1467584411, 1269576253, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 3, 0);
