(30, 2, 1, 1, 0, 'Mobile UI Update', '<p>I have started to make UI updates to support mobile. The GrokBB homepage, Search, Quick Tour, Create Your Own Community, Messages, and Top 100 pages now display properly on smaller screen sizes. I will be working on the board pages next (i.e. board homepage, viewing a topic, etc) and hopefully have that wrapped up over the weekend.</p>\n<p>I am only doing a quick first pass right now, just enough to make the site usable in mobile so that we can attract more users. Also, I am only testing on iPad and iPhone. I will be testing on more devices and doing the more complicated pages when we get to the mobile phase in the roadmap.</p>\n', 'I have started to make UI updates to support mobile. The GrokBB homepage, Search, Quick Tour, Create Your Own Community, Messages, and Top 100 pages now display properly on smaller screen sizes. I will be working on the board pages next (i.e. board homepage, viewing a topic, etc) and hopefully have that wrapped up over the weekend.\n\nI am only doing a quick first pass right now, just enough to make the site usable in mobile so that we can attract more users. Also, I am only testing on iPad and iPhone. I will be testing on more devices and doing the more complicated pages when we get to the mobile phase in the roadmap.', 1466848432, 1269576253, 1466848579, 1269576253, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', 41, 2),
