(36, 2, 1, 1, 0, 'New Feature - Who is Online, RSS and Mentions (the @ Symbol)', '<p>I will be adding a few new features over the holiday ...</p>\n<ul><li>a new Sidebar option to display what users are currently browsing your board</li>\n<li>a new Sidebar link that will allow users to subscribe to a RSS feed for new topics</li>\n<li>the ability to mention a user in a reply with the @ symbol, which will cause them to get notified of your post</li>\n</ul>', 'I will be adding a few new features over the holiday ...\n\n* a new Sidebar option to display what users are currently browsing your board\n* a new Sidebar link that will allow users to subscribe to a RSS feed for new topics\n* the ability to mention a user in a reply with the @ symbol, which will cause them to get notified of your post', 1467578425, 1269576253, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', 34, 6),
