(41, 2, 1, 1, 0, 'New Feature - Media in Topics', '<p>I have added a new feature that lets you add pictures, videos and audio to topics. You can do this by adding links to the "Your Media" section, underneath the Markdown editor, when creating or editing a topic. The first media file will automatically get displayed under your content, and a thumbnail will get created that is displayed next to your topic when users are browsing the board. If you add more then one media file than a slideshow becomes available too.</p>\n<p>Here is an example ...</p>\n', 'I have added a new feature that lets you add pictures, videos and audio to topics. You can do this by adding links to the "Your Media" section, underneath the Markdown editor, when creating or editing a topic. The first media file will automatically get displayed under your content, and a thumbnail will get created that is displayed next to your topic when users are browsing the board. If you add more then one media file than a slideshow becomes available too.\n\nHere is an example ...\n\n', 1468318527, 1269576253, 1469167372, 1269576253, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', 39, 1);
